plot: Supergirl continues to fight Nyxly for the remaining totems but after Nyxly kidnaps William, Supergirl realizes she needs to take a more proactive stance to keep National City safe. Meanwhile, Alex faces the biggest challenge of her life.

Nyxyl tries to get the Hope Totem, and the Super Friends try to hold the world together when hope is lost. Kelly and Alex deal with their first day as mothers when Esme fears that her new family will abandon her, and Nxyly realizes that there is an easier way to get the Totems stealing them one at a time.—Gislef
